Installation Instructions
*************************

Build Dependencies
==================

- `clang` with C++11
- `libc++`
- `pkg-config`
- `bison` and `flex`

Basic Installation
==================

- `git clone ...`
- `git submodule init`
- `git submodule update`
- Type `./autogen.sh`.
- Type `./configure && make`.
- Type `make install` to install.
